#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;⑥ Selection选择；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;⑦ Solid Result业绩能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;7、 业绩猛增的5类销售人员&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;① 导师型：靠智慧吃饭的带队者；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;② 斗士型：喜欢交谈、擅长外交，喜欢与销售并肩作战；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;③ 警官型：有极高的忠诚度；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;④ 自信型：没有“不可能”；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;⑤ 事必躬亲型：有强烈的责任感。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;8、 销售三境界&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1、围人：能将顾客围住，并死缠烂打，初步具备接近顾客、推介购买的能力；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;2、维人：建立长期稳定的关系，不是简单的买卖关系，而是朋友、伙伴关系；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;3、为人：不只是把产品卖出去，同时把自己也销售出去。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;9、 乐观销售更容易接近和打动顾客&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1、乐观的人发现工作和生活中的真善美，到哪里都是“阳光使者”；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;2、销售就是信心的传递和信念的转移；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;3、乐观的销售让顾客获得快乐的消费体验，更容易跟你交往和敞开心扉；&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;4、乐观的销售更能战胜挫折,发现事物积极一面&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '0', '1631073436', '0');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('10146', '1', '4', '', '一套可以拿去直接用的社区营销方案', 'http://www.lovephp.com/example/article/thumb/10146.jpg', '社群是包含了公众号内容运营、小程序服务承载、个人朋友圈打造+一对一私聊、微信群活动策划等一系列板块在内的综合性私域流量解决方案', '&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 0px&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;社交直播流行起来，社群越来越火，几乎成了每个主播的标配，尤其是受这次疫情影响，线下实体店老板损失惨重，都在寻求线上转型。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;不可否认，短视频、直播是当前最火热的概念，但是社群是持续运营和转化客户的必备战场&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;这个地方，需要纠正一下很多人的误区，&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;社群≠微信群&lt;/span&gt;，社群是包含了公众号内容运营、小程序服务承载、个人朋友圈打造+一对一私聊、微信群活动策划等一系列板块在内的综合性私域流量解决方案&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href&#x3d;&quot;https://www.aikeyuan.cn&quot; target&#x3d;&quot;_self&quot; title&#x3d;&quot;爱客源-找电话查客源,精准获客营销助手&quot;&gt;&lt;img src&#x3d;&quot;http://www.lovephp.com/example/article/image/20210908/1631074269442225.jpg&quot; title&#x3d;&quot;1631074269442225.jpg&quot; alt&#x3d;&quot;src&#x3d;http___eww.jnzcly.albiz.cn_imgMsg88_images_201609_14726918991813.jpg&amp;refer&#x3d;http___eww.jnzcly.albiz.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;很多社群运营者往往会经历三个阶段：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;看不起，瞧不上&lt;br/&gt;这还不简单，不就是拉个群，发发广告，维护一下老客户嘛，这个简单&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;看不懂，学不会&lt;br/&gt;拉完群，卧槽，群里怎么没人说话？搞秒杀，哎呀，怎么没人买呢？脑壳疼&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;懂理论，会实操&lt;br/&gt;系统学习，踩坑无数，学成下山，最终应付自如，笑笑心说：不过如此&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;很多老板，之前没实操过社群，完全处于懵逼状态，油锅里捞金——&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;无从下手&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;所以，石头写了一篇社群运营方案的模板，供大家参考，社群路上不迷路&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;不会操作怎么办？&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;先模仿，后原创，照猫画虎，看看人家怎么搞的，比着做，说到这，&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;有经验的老板们，会心一笑：奶奶的，你真“坏”，不过，我很喜欢&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;好了，废话不多说，直接开始干货部分&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;一.市场调研&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;兵马未动，粮草先行。在运营社群之前，要先做充足的市场调研，&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;了解目标用户人群画像，他们在哪里，喜欢什么，有什么痛点，&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;需要解决什么问题，才好对症下药&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;通过市场调研要解决以下问题&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;成交产品&lt;br/&gt;产品价格&lt;br/&gt;人群画像&lt;br/&gt;用户评价&lt;br/&gt;用户痛点&lt;br/&gt;竞品分析&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1.通过&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;百度指数、360趋势、微信指数、5118&lt;/span&gt;等了解他们大致的年龄、性别、区域分布&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;2.通过电商平台数据，分析目标人群关心什么，有什么样的痛点&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;① 看评价标签，差评，可以看出来核心卖点&lt;br/&gt;② 看手淘问大家，可以看出来用户真正关心的问题&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b;&quot;&gt;二.确定社群目标&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;不同的目标，侧重点不同，需要针对制定方案&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;① 群内线上直接成交利润款产品，侧重于成交额和利润率&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;② 群内成交低价引流款产品，侧重于引流客户到店消费&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;三.种子用户获取&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;精准鱼塘+超级诱饵&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;找到目标人群所在的精准鱼塘，释放超级诱饵，吸引客户添加微信&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;三.种子用户获取&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;精准鱼塘+超级诱饵&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;找到目标人群所在的精准鱼塘，释放超级诱饵，吸引客户添加微信&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class&#x3d;&quot;ztext-empty-paragraph&quot; style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: -0.8em&#x3b; margin-bottom: -0.8em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;② 群内爆粉&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;这种方式适用于，转化周期长的产品，配合朋友圈+一对一私聊，先培养基础信任，后续做转化。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;使用&lt;a href&#x3d;&quot;https://www.aikeyuan.cn&quot; target&#x3d;&quot;_self&quot; title&#x3d;&quot;爱客源-找电话查客源,精准获客营销助手&quot;&gt;爱客源&lt;/a&gt;www.aikeyuan.cn工具，目前，我用这种方法，10个号，一天可以加&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;300-500&lt;/span&gt;，这种方式，操作细节比较多&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;③ 截流涨粉&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;这个我有实际操作，对微信账号有要求，并且要辅助软件，批量化操作&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;④ 换群涨粉&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;先加一些基础的用户，然后让这些用户拉你进2-3个群，每进一个群发个1-2元红包，每个群，可以被动涨粉，过来的人，再让他拉你进2-3个群。循环往复，直至裂变到自己想要的基础流量&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;群内某大佬就是靠这个看似很笨的方法，&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;3个月搞了10万宝妈粉&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;2.内容涨粉&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;① 发帖引流&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;有人的地方就有流量，贴吧、豆瓣、简书、小红书，顺应平台规则，&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;小规模测试路径，大规模复制引流&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;② 内容干货引流&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;优质的内容是流量的永动机，内容干货引流是成本最低，质量最高的引流方式，但是时间周期长，操作要求高，建议长线布局内容矩阵&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;四.超级诱饵和海报设置&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1.诱饵：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;选择低成本高价值产品，宝妈群体&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;实物&lt;/span&gt;比虚拟物品更有吸引力，知识付费群体资料包是引流神器&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;敲黑板：推荐&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;淘客高佣&lt;/span&gt;，非常有用&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;2.海报设计：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;海报文案的4个套路：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;痛点型：恐惧性的问题描述+解决方案&lt;br/&gt;权威型：知名品牌或吸睛头衔+分享内容&lt;br/&gt;获得型：产品名+身体获得/心理获得/财富获得&lt;br/&gt;速成型：耗费时间少/学习任务少+呈现效果&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;海报设计的6大要素：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;喜好：禀赋效应，损失规避&lt;br/&gt;权威：专业性，名校名企，大咖推荐&lt;br/&gt;从众：利他心理，社会认同&lt;br/&gt;承诺：求快心理，获得心理，行动效果&lt;br/&gt;互惠：价格锚点，占便宜心理&lt;br/&gt;稀缺：紧迫感，专属感&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-color: rgb&#x28;255, 255, 255&#x29;&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b;&quot;&gt;五、裂变&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif&#x3b; font-size: medium&#x3b; white-space: normal&#x3b; background-colo