#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;12,439&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;53&lt;/th&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;10,764&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;10,753&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;10,934&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;平均日销售&lt;/th&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;10,546&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;10,508&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;11,114&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;10,443&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;10,869&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;11,750&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;11,133&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;blockquote style&#x3d;&quot;margin: 1.4em 0px&#x3b; padding-left: 1em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;100, 100, 100&#x29;&#x3b; border-left: 3px solid rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;&gt;4.找出平均日销售最低那天的销售数据，把它的日权重指数设为1.00，然后用剩余六天的日销售额除以这个最低值，得到每天的日权重指数。&lt;br/&gt;5.将每天的日权重指数相加得出周权重指数。如表：&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;table width&#x3d;&quot;690&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class&#x3d;&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;星期一&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;星期二&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;星期三&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;星期四&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;星期五&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;星期六&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;星期日&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;合计&lt;/th&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;平均日销售&lt;/th&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;10,546&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;10,508&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;11,114&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;10,443&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;10,869&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;11,750&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;11,133&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;76,363&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 235, 235&#x29;&#x3b; font-weight: 500&#x3b;&quot;&gt;日权重指数&lt;/th&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1.01&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1.01&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1.06&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1.00&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1.04&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1.13&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1.07&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b;&quot;&gt;7.31&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b; color: rgb&#x28;18, 18, 18&#x29;&#x3b; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;&gt;该店的周权重指数为7.31，日权重指数最高的是周六，最低的是周四，整体浮动区间较小。&lt;/p&gt;二、权重指数的应用&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b;&quot;&gt;有了权重指数之后，可以用来&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b; font-synthesis: style&#x3b;&quot;&gt;对比销售情况&lt;/span&gt;，&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b; font-synthesis: style&#x3b;&quot;&gt;月度销售预测&lt;/span&gt;以及&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b; font-synthesis: style&#x3b;&quot;&gt;分解销售目标&lt;/span&gt;（本次分析不做销售目标分解）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style&#x3d;&quot;margin: 0px 0px calc&#x28;1.27273em&#x29;&#x3b; font-style: inherit&#x3b; font-variant: inherit&#x3b; font-stretch: inherit&#x3b; font-size: 1.1em&#x3b; line-height: 1.5&#x3b; font-family: inherit&#x3b; clear: left&#x3b; font-synthesis: style&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-synthesis: style&#x3b;&quot;&gt;1.对比销售&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b;&quot;&gt;这里引入一个新指标，单位权重销售值，将某个时期内平均单位权重指数的销售额，这样就在对比日销售数据时将权重值考虑到其中。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style&#x3d;&quot;font-weight: 600&#x3b; font-synthesis: style&#x3b;&quot;&gt;单位权重销售值&#x3d;日销售额÷日权重值&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style&#x3d;&quot;margin-top: 1.4em&#x3b; margin-bottom: 1.4em&#x3b;&quot;&gt;这里分析门店D在2021年11月1日-24日的销售情况，引入权重指数和单位权重销售值。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width&#x3d;&quot;690&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class&#x3d;&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;th style&#x3d;&quot;border-color: rgb&#x28;211, 211, 211&#x29;&#x3b; line-height: 24px&#x3b; height: 24px&#x3b; padding: 3px 12px&#x3b; background: rgb&#x28;235, 23